org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.scheduler.placement

Interface SchedulingPlacementSet<N extends SchedulerNode>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalitySchedulingPlacementSet

    public interface SchedulingPlacementSet<N extends SchedulerNode>

    Comparing to PlacementSet, this also maintains pending ResourceRequests: - When new ResourceRequest(s) added to scheduler, or, - Or new container allocated, scheduler can notify corresponding PlacementSet.

    Different set of resource requests (E.g., resource requests with the same schedulerKey) can have one instance of PlacementSet, each PlacementSet can have different ways to order nodes depends on requests.
